<materialsCitation pageId="62" pageNumber="546">
“El Sauce Peralta, a farm on the Atlantic railroad,less than halfway from San Jose to 
<collectingRegion box="[2104,2196,1893,1926]" country="Costa Rica" name="Limon" pageId="62" pageNumber="546">Limon</collectingRegion>
, probably about 
<quantity box="[2435,2558,1893,1926]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.048" pageId="62" pageNumber="546" unit="ft" value="1000.0">1000 feet</quantity>
[= 
